title: Two Bedroom Apartment For Rent! Reserve at Hyde Park Today!!!
posting_body: ['Two Bedroom Apartment Available at Hyde Park!', 'Reserve Now!', 'Close to shopping, golfing, parks and bicycle trails, Hyde Park Apartments is the perfect solution for affordable living in close proximity to everything you need to live comfortably.', 'At Hyde Park Apartments, you can enjoy a swimming pool and air conditioned comfort during warm weather and year-round you will love the small-community feel of each of our 4 buildings with just 17 units each.', ' All units are accessed from indoor hallways, so you will feel secure in your apartment home.', ' Courtesy Patrol is also available nightly.', ' The best part of coming home to Hyde Park is knowing that you live in a clean, well maintained community that is close to everything and also happens to be one of the best rent bargains in town.', 'Community Features:', 'Outdoor Pool', 'Laundry room is on the first floor only', 'Apartment Features:', 'Water Heated', 'Electric Stove', 'Window Treatments', 'Carpet', 'Air Conditioning', 'Pet policy:', 'Cats allowed, Dogs not accepted', "Rental criteria: UD's, criminal and convictions not accepted.", 'Hyde Park Apts', 'show contact info', '1354 7th St NW', 'New Brighton, MN, 55112']
